{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "spectacular-sven-scenes",
    "category": "movie",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VqvHvwi32pk&t=29s",
    "mode": "cues_rebuild"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, I'm out!",
      "zh": "好了，我出去了！",
      "ja": "よし、出るよ！",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whoa!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "うわっ！",
      "time": "00:00:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, my God!",
      "zh": "天啊！",
      "ja": "なんてこった！",
      "time": "00:00:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, Sven, I didn't get your carrots.",
      "zh": "不，斯溫，我沒有拿你的胡蘿蔔。",
      "ja": "違うよ、スヴェン、君のニンジンは取ってないよ。",
      "time": "00:00:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But I did find a place to sleep.",
      "zh": "但我找到了一個睡覺的地方。",
      "ja": "でも寝る場所は見つけたよ。",
      "time": "00:00:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And it's free.",
      "zh": "而且是免費的。",
      "ja": "しかも無料だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Rain tears are better than people.",
      "zh": "雨水的眼淚比人還好。",
      "ja": "雨の涙は人間よりマシだよ。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sven, don't you think that's true?",
      "zh": "斯溫，你不覺得這是真的嗎？",
      "ja": "スヴェン、それは本当だと思わない？",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, people will beat you and curse you and cheat you.",
      "zh": "是啊，人們會打你、罵你、騙你。",
      "ja": "そうだね、人は君を殴ったり、罵ったり、騙したりするよ。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Every one of them's bound.",
      "zh": "他們每一個都會這樣。",
      "ja": "みんなそうするんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Except you.",
      "zh": "除了你。",
      "ja": "君を除いてね。",
      "time": "00:00:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, thanks, buddy.",
      "zh": "哦，謝了，夥伴。",
      "ja": "ああ、ありがとう、相棒。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course, I don't want to help her anymore.",
      "zh": "當然，我不想再幫她了。",
      "ja": "もちろん、もう彼女を助けたくない。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "In fact, this whole thing has ruined me for helping anyone ever again.",
      "zh": "事實上，這整件事讓我再也不想幫任何人了。",
      "ja": "実際、この一件で誰も助けたくなくなった。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So die on her own?",
      "zh": "所以讓她自己死去？",
      "ja": "じゃあ彼女を一人で死なせるの？",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can live with that.",
      "zh": "我可以接受。",
      "ja": "それなら仕方ない。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But you won't get your new sled if she's dead.",
      "zh": "但如果她死了，你就拿不到新雪橇了。",
      "ja": "でも彼女が死んだら新しいそりはもらえないよ。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sometimes I really don't like you.",
      "zh": "有時候我真的不喜歡你。",
      "ja": "時々本当に君のことが嫌いだ。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, hold up!",
      "zh": "喔，等等！",
      "ja": "おっと、待って！",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're coming!",
      "zh": "我們來了！",
      "ja": "行くよ！",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You are?",
      "zh": "你們嗎？",
      "ja": "君たち？",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I mean, sure!",
      "zh": "當然！",
      "ja": "もちろん！",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, I'll let you tag along.",
      "zh": "是的，我讓你們一起來。",
      "ja": "うん、一緒に来ていいよ。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "zh": "喔，不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いや。",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And you are...",
      "zh": "你是...",
      "ja": "君は…",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, um, I'm Anna.",
      "zh": "喔，嗯，我是安娜。",
      "ja": "ああ、えっと、私はアンナです。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And who's the funky looking donkey over there?",
      "zh": "那邊那隻看起來怪怪的驢子是誰？",
      "ja": "あそこにいる変な見た目のロバは誰？",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's Sven.",
      "zh": "那是斯溫。",
      "ja": "それはスヴェンだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "zh": "嗯哼。",
      "ja": "うんうん。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And who's the reindeer?",
      "zh": "那馴鹿是誰？",
      "ja": "そしてあのトナカイは誰？",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sven?",
      "zh": "斯溫？",
      "ja": "スヴェン？",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, they're...",
      "zh": "哦，他們是...",
      "ja": "ああ、彼らは…",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Make things easier for me.",
      "zh": "讓我好辦事。",
      "ja": "楽にしてくれ。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All I could have tried to kidce my notes.",
      "zh": "我只能試著記下我的筆記。",
      "ja": "メモを取ろうとしただけだ。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like you too.",
      "zh": "我也喜歡你。",
      "ja": "僕も君が好きだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, love.",
      "zh": "哦，親愛的。",
      "ja": "ああ、愛しい人。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did Elsa build you?",
      "zh": "艾莎造了你嗎？",
      "ja": "エルサが作ったの？",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, why?",
      "zh": "是啊，為什麼？",
      "ja": "うん、どうして？",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you know where she is?",
      "zh": "你知道她在哪裡嗎？",
      "ja": "彼女がどこにいるか知ってる？",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, yes, why?",
      "zh": "知道，知道，為什麼？",
      "ja": "うん、うん、どうして？",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you think you could show us the way?",
      "zh": "你能帶我們去嗎？",
      "ja": "道を教えてくれる？",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, why?",
      "zh": "是啊，為什麼？",
      "ja": "うん、どうして？",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How does this work?",
      "zh": "這怎麼用？",
      "ja": "これはどうやって使うの？",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ow!",
      "zh": "哎呦！",
      "ja": "痛っ！",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stop, it's Sven.",
      "zh": "停，這是斯溫。",
      "ja": "やめて、スヴェンだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Try and focus here.",
      "zh": "試著專心點。",
      "ja": "ここに集中して。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, uh...",
      "zh": "哦，呃...",
      "ja": "ああ、えっと…",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What is it, buddy?",
      "zh": "怎麼了，夥伴？",
      "ja": "どうしたんだ、相棒？",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey!",
      "zh": "嘿！",
      "ja": "おい！",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Watch it.",
      "zh": "小心點。",
      "ja": "気をつけて。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's run with you.",
      "zh": "讓我們跟你一起跑。",
      "ja": "一緒に走ろう。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't understand you only when you talk like that.",
      "zh": "我只有在你這樣說話時才懂你。",
      "ja": "君がそう話す時だけ分かるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stop it!",
      "zh": "別這樣！",
      "ja": "やめて！",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Put me down!",
      "zh": "放我下來！",
      "ja": "降ろして！",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, Sven.",
      "zh": "不，斯溫。",
      "ja": "ダメだ、スヴェン。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We're not going back.",
      "zh": "我們不會回去的。",
      "ja": "戻らないよ。",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She's with her true love.",
      "zh": "她和她的真愛在一起。",
      "ja": "彼女は本当の愛と一緒だ。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What the...",
      "zh": "這是...",
      "ja": "なんだって…",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Anna...",
      "zh": "安娜...",
      "ja": "アンナ…",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What the...",
      "zh": "這是...",
      "ja": "なんだって…",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, okay.",
      "zh": "好，好。",
      "ja": "わかった、わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here we are.",
      "zh": "我們到了。",
      "ja": "着いたよ。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I owe you a sled.",
      "zh": "我欠你一台雪橇。",
      "ja": "そりを借りてるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "zh": "喔，不。",
      "ja": "ああ、いや。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you serious?",
      "zh": "你是認真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本気？",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's the latest model.",
      "zh": "這是最新款。",
      "ja": "最新モデルだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, I can't accept this.",
      "zh": "不，我不能接受這個。",
      "ja": "いや、これは受け取れない。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You have to.",
      "zh": "你必須接受。",
      "ja": "受け取らなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No returns.",
      "zh": "不退貨。",
      "ja": "返品不可。",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No exchanges.",
      "zh": "不換貨。",
      "ja": "交換不可。",
      "time": "00:02:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Queen's orders.",
      "zh": "女王的命令。",
      "ja": "女王の命令だ。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She's named you the official errand and ice master and deliverer.",
      "zh": "她任命你為官方差使和冰雪大師及送貨員。",
      "ja": "彼女は君を公式の使いと氷の達人、配達人に任命した。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "你好。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Got it!",
      "zh": "明白了！",
      "ja": "了解！",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Some things never change.",
      "zh": "有些事情永遠不變。",
      "ja": "変わらないこともある。",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like the love that I feel for her.",
      "zh": "就像我對她的愛。",
      "ja": "彼女への愛のように。",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Some things stay the same.",
      "zh": "有些事情保持不變。",
      "ja": "変わらないこともある。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like how rings are easier.",
      "zh": "就像戒指更簡單。",
      "ja": "指輪の方が簡単なように。",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But if I commit and I go for it,",
      "zh": "但如果我承諾並努力，",
      "ja": "でも、もし決心して挑戦すれば、",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll know what to say and do.",
      "zh": "我會知道該說什麼和做什麼。",
      "ja": "何を言い、何をすべきか分かるだろう。",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Right?",
      "zh": "對吧？",
      "ja": "そうだよね？",
      "time": "00:03:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Some things never change.",
      "zh": "有些事情永遠不變。",
      "ja": "変わらないこともある。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sven, the pressure is all on you.",
      "zh": "斯溫，壓力全在你身上。",
      "ja": "スヴェン、プレッシャーは全部君にかかってる。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What a his memory.",
      "zh": "他的記憶真好。",
      "ja": "なんて記憶力だ。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The water that makes up you and me has passed through at least four humans and our animals before us.",
      "zh": "構成你我身體的水，曾經流經至少四個人類和我們的動物。",
      "ja": "君と僕を作る水は、僕たちの前に少なくとも4人の人間と動物を通ってきた。",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And remembers everything.",
      "zh": "並且記得一切。",
      "ja": "そしてすべてを覚えている。",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The bend back.",
      "zh": "彎回去。",
      "ja": "戻れ。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, delicious.",
      "zh": "不，美味。",
      "ja": "いや、美味しい。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think I'll name you.",
      "zh": "我想給你取名。",
      "ja": "名前をつけようと思う。",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Gail.",
      "zh": "蓋爾。",
      "ja": "ゲイル。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah.",
      "zh": "啊。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Rangiers are better than people.",
      "zh": "馴鹿比人好。",
      "ja": "トナカイは人間よりいい。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sven, why is love so hard?",
      "zh": "斯溫，為什麼愛情這麼難？",
      "ja": "スヴェン、なぜ愛はこんなに難しいの？",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You feel what you feel and those feelings are real.",
      "zh": "你感受到的就是你的感覺，那些感覺是真實的。",
      "ja": "感じるものは本物の感情だよ。",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on, Christoph.",
      "zh": "加油，克里斯托夫。",
      "ja": "さあ、クリストフ。",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let down your guard.",
      "zh": "放下你的防備。",
      "ja": "警戒を解いて。",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "God.",
